<para0><title>SERVICING PRECAUTIONS</title>
<para>The following are servicing precautions:</para>
<step1><para>Aircraft shall be safe for maintenance in accordance
with <extref targetdoc="itod10jg001" targetid="itod10jg001"
displayvalue="TO 1F-16( )-2-10JG-00-1">.</para>
</step1>
<step1><para>Refer to <extref targetdoc="itod12jg001"
targetid="itod12jg001" displayvalue="TO 1F-16( )-2-12JG-00-1"> for
safety requirements and protective gear.</para>
</step1>
</para0>
